Fern Hollow~
Thick ferns blanket the hollow floor, their fronds brushing knee-height on the trail through here. @@GFresh animal tracks crisscross the damp soil between the fern stems.@@N The hollow stays shaded even in full afternoon when sun breaks through the canopy. The silence here is deep and pleasant.
